00111 /* operation codes for EulerOp */
00112 enum opcode
00113 {
00114    MVSF,                               /* make vertex solid shell face */
00115    KVSF,                               /* kill vertex solid shell face */
00116    MEV,                                /* make edge vertex             */
00117    KEV,                                /* kill edge vertex             */
00118    MEF,                                /* make edge face               */
00119    KEF,                                /* kill edge face               */
00120    KEMR,                               /* kill edge make ring          */
00121    MEKR,                               /* make edge kill ring          */
00122    KFMRH,                              /* kill face make ring hole     */
00123    MFKRH,                              /* make face kill ring hole     */
00124    MSFKR,                              /* make shell face kill ring    */
00125    KSFMR,                              /* kill shell face make ring    */
00126    HARDREM,                            /* hard remove                  */
00127    RMOVE,                              /* ring move                    */
00128    NEWLOC,                             /* locate vertex coordinates    */
00129    REVERT,                             /* revert topology              */
00130    MODIFYNAMES,                        /* modify names for Boolean     */
00131    MERGE,                              /* merge operation              */
00132    DETACH,                             /* detach operation             */
00133    TRANS,                              /* translation                  */
00134    ROTAT,                              /* rotation                     */
00135    SCALE,                              /* scale                        */
00136    TRANSFORM,                          /* transformation               */
00137    ASSOCIATE,                          /* association between elements */
00138    CRTAXSTRS,                          /* create axis of translation   */
00139    CRTAXSROT,                          /* create axis of rotation      */
00140    CRTGRP,                             /* create group                 */
00141    REMAXS,                             /* remove axis                  */
00142    REMGRP,                             /* remove group                 */
00143    MOVAXIS,                            /* move axis of rotation        */
00144    ROTAXIS,                            /* rotate an axis               */
00145    SETGRP,                             /* set current group            */
00146    COLOR,                              /* set color of a solid/group   */
00147    NAME,                               /* set name of solid/group/axis */
00148 
00149 #ifdef __curved_env__
00150    SETCTAG,                            /* define a tag curve           */
00151    SETSTAG,                            /* define a tag surface         */
00152    NEWLINE,                            /* create geometric line        */
00153    KILLLINE,                           /* kill geometric line          */
00154    NEWPOLY,                            /* create geom. polyline        */
00155    KILLPOLY,                           /* kill geometric polyline      */
00156    ADDLPOINT,                          /* add point to polyline        */
00157    REMLPOINT,                          /* remove point from polyline   */
00158    NEWPLANE,                           /* create geometric plane       */
00159    KILLPLANE,                          /* kill geometric plane         */
00160    NEWCYLINDER,                        /* create geom. cylinder        */
00161    KILLCYLINDER,                       /* kill geometric cylinder      */
00162    NEWCONE,                            /* create geometric cone        */
00163    KILLCONE,                           /* kill geometric cone          */
00164    NEWSPHERE,                          /* create geometric sphere      */
00165    KILLSPHERE,                         /* kill geometric sphere        */
00166    NEWTORUS,                           /* create geometric torus       */
00167    KILLTORUS,                          /* kill geometric torus         */
00168    NEWROTSURF,                         /* create rotational surf.      */
00169    KILLROTSURF,                        /* kill rotational surf.        */
00170    NEWBLENDSURF,                       /* create blend surface         */
00171    KILLBLENDSURF,                      /* kill blend surface           */
00172 #endif
00173    MAXCODE,                            /* largest opcode assigned      */
00174 };
